UK Primary Care Network is a leading source of diabetes news, expert insight
and knowledge for primary healthcare professionals. The network is free-to-
join and provides impartial, trustworthy content that helps improve patient
>>>>>>> When you sign-up to the Primary Care Network, you gain access to a
range of content and resources that support both you and your patients.
